  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbf \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "People blocked the road in Mannar demanding cooking gas",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Bengali villagers of Mannar, Nanatan Divisional Secretary took out a public demonstration today Saturday (16) morning demanding cooking gas.",
        "A few days ago around 900 liters of cooking gas was distributed to the public at the Mannar public playground.",
        "However today (16) was not distributed to Bengali village but was distributed to other villages.",
        "In this situation, people belonging to 4 village officer units in Bengali village blocked the main road of Bengali and started protesting with gas cylinders.",
        "During this the villagers expressed their problems to the police officer and handed over a letter containing the demand stating that their village was being neglected from the cooking gas supply operations.",
        "In this situation, the said police officer informed the Mannar district government president about the matter and promised to take action to provide cooking gas on the coming Wednesday (20).",
        "In this situation, as per the request of the police, the people left the place without blocking the road."
      ],
